 JELL 
 
 JACK 
 This isnt a question of whether or not you are 
 the right person to be true. I have no need to 
 stand in my way through. 
 
 The boy tries to move past the camera. Bashir keeps 
 trying to hang out some of it. 
 
 JACK 
 All right. Lets get back 
